Fullstack Developer
-------------------

I am a fullstack developer with 4 years of experience working with the MERN stack, developing scalable NodeJS apps using the AWS serverless architecture. I am currently working as a Backend developer for [@littledata](https://github.com/littledata), fixing your e-commerce analytics one commit at a time.

* 🌍  I'm based in Bucharest
* ✉️  You can contact me at [george@littledata.io](mailto:george@littledata.io)
* 🧠  I'm learning IoT, Raspberry Pi, Electronics
* 🤝  I'm open to collaborating on IoT Projects
